channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Report: Brazil Could Ditch Nike as Kit Supplier After Receiving Massive Offer
item.description: Brazilian news outlet reports CBF has received an offer worth more than five times what Nike currently pays them from either Adidas or Puma

item.title: 'DWTS' Cheryl Burke Plans 40th Birthday By Herself, Friends Don't Care
item.description: Cheryl Burke is turning 40, but is planning a party by herself and for herself -- the reason being, according to her, is that her good pals don't give a rip ... and she's salty about it. The "Dancing With the Stars" alum threw up a TikTok this week…

item.title: USL’s Orange County Try to Capture Magic with New Cup Kit
item.description: Kit is inspired by designs worn in 1910s, when U.S. Open Cup started, and will be worn when OCSC takes on Loudoun United in Round of 32 on Tuesday, May 7

item.title: Kendall Jenner Reunites with Bad Bunny at Met Gala, Same Hotel
item.description: Kendall Jenner seems to be back with Bad Bunny -- at least that's what it looked like at the Met Gala ... where they were seen getting cozy, and possibly even staying at the same hotel. The model and pop star were photographed hanging out at an…

item.title: Panama Football Unveils New National Team Crest
item.description: Crest depicts a harpy eagle — the national bird of Panama — with each feather representing one of the country's 10 provinces

item.title: Snoop Dogg’s Gin & Juice Brand Becomes Presenting Sponsor of Arizona Bowl
item.description: The Arizona Bowl announced a multi-year partnership with 17-time Grammy Award winning artist Snoop Dogg that makes his alcohol brand, Gin & Juice by Dre and Snoop, the game’s presenting sponsor.

item.title: Bayern Munich Goes All In On Red With 2024-25 Home Kits
item.description: Sponsor logo on left sleeve contains QR code that fans can scan to participate in exclusive promotions throughout the 2024-25 season
